      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. one thing though, i've heard the train stations in tokyo can be super confusing and crowded. specifically the transfer between the lines near shibuya. is there any way to make the commute from marunouchi to shibuya a bit more predictable? i'm worried about getting lost in the stations or stuck in the crowds.",
